Privacy Policy for Subliminal Affirmations Flasher
Effective Date: July 18, 2025

1. Data Collection
This extension does not collect, store, or transmit any personal or sensitive user data. All settings and affirmations are kept only on your device.

2. Local Storage
Your preferences and affirmations are saved locally using Chromeâ€™s storage system. This allows the extension to remember your settings between sessions.

3. No Third-Party Services
The extension does not use any third-party services, tracking tools, analytics, or advertising networks.

4. Permissions
The permissions requested (such as storage, scripting, and tabs) are only used to flash affirmations on webpages. No other activity is performed.

5. Security
All extension code runs locally. No external or remote code is used. This helps protect your privacy and keep the extension secure.

6. Contact
If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, please email: your.email@example.com

By using this extension, you agree to this privacy policy.


